\
\
Greed. This is the most deceptive one of them all. It is the one our hearts resist to admit the most. It is easy to admit gluttony or pride or lust. These can be easily seen the mirror of scripture but greed become camouflaged many different excuses including 'need'. behind But to admit we are greedy is to admit we must change where we put our trust and hope in. \
\
Illustration of me spending money I was going to get 1500 different ways before I even got it. I was obsessed with what I could do with it. It was fun to fantisize about what if's. Most of us have had an experience like that. Maybe for you it's around tax return season or year end bonus season. It's easy to allow our minds to wander into greed accidently. \
